---
title: Rigatoni “a la Vodka” with Pancetta, Spinach, and Herby Breadcrumbs
description: Okay, so there’s technically no vodka in this recipe, but that can be our secret. The combination of creamy tomato sauce and salty pancetta is flavorful enough without it! Serve straight from the skillet for a way easier cleanup.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatoni-a-la-vodka-family-e5124969.jpg
